Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: dockit
Version: 0.1.5
Summary: Fuzzy current location to git pull with all submodules or launch, close and exec container through docker-compose.
Home-page: https://github.com/Ron-Chang/dockit.git
Author: Ron Chang
Author-email: ron.hsien.chang@gmail.com
License: MIT
Description: # Dockit
        ## - What is this?
        Fuzzy the current location or appoint specific project name to
        - git
          + pull repository and all submodules
        
        - docker
          + launch the same prefix service with current project
          + close the same prefix service with current project
          + execute the container with the same as project
        
        ## - History
        
        |#|      date|                                            version|
        |-|----------|---------------------------------------------------|
        |1|2020/01/24| [v0.1.2](https://github.com/Ron-Chang/dockit#v012)|
